WEBVTT

00:00:27.833 --> 00:00:32.476
Let's raise our voices to welcome
renowned social scientist and author

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:34.101
Deepa Narayan.

00:00:34.125 --> 00:00:36.351
(Music)

00:00:36.375 --> 00:00:40.292
(Applause)

00:00:44.708 --> 00:00:46.893
Deepa Narayan: The goal
of every loving parent

00:00:46.917 --> 00:00:48.768
is to raise good girls,

00:00:48.792 --> 00:00:50.601
but what parents actually do

00:00:50.625 --> 00:00:55.143
is to constrain, confine
and crush their girls.

00:00:55.167 --> 00:00:57.018
So as they crush their girls,

00:00:57.042 --> 00:00:58.958
they prepare them for abuse.

00:00:59.875 --> 00:01:02.059
This would be so devastating